p; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-display\">display</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Options Sets</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.overview.sponsor\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.sponsor </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-sponsor-cs#bhp (\"Behavioral Health and Performance\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.overview.discipline\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.discipline </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-discipline-cs#behavioral (\"Behavior and Performance\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-activities.personnel\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-activities.personnel </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-roles-cs#crewmember (\"Crewmember\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-roles-cs#bhp-specialist (\"BHP Specialist\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-activities.location\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-activities.location </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-facility-cs#jsc (\"Johnson Space Center\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-facility-cs#russia-gctc (\"Gagarin Cosmonaut Training Center\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.assessment-results.behavioral-readiness\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for assessment-results.behavioral-readiness </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">http://snomed.info/sct#17621005 (\"Normal\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">http://snomed.info/sct#263654008 (\"Abnormal\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Cleared with conditions</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Not cleared</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.behavioral-metrics.coping-capacity\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for behavioral-metrics.coping-capacity </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Excellent</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Good</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Adequate</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Marginal</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Inadequate</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.behavioral-metrics.sleep-quality\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for behavioral-metrics.sleep-quality </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Excellent</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Good</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Fair</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Poor</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.behavioral-metrics.cognitive-readiness\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for behavioral-metrics.cognitive-readiness </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Fully ready</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Ready with minor concerns</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Ready with monitoring</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Not ready</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.behavioral-metrics.social-connectedness\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for behavioral-metrics.social-connectedness </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Strong</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Adequate</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Weak</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Concerning</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#emr (\"Electronic Medical Record\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
